      {type:'key', heading:'🌊 The First Civilizations',
       text:`The oldest known civilizations are: <span class="key-word" data-def="The civilization of ancient Egypt, famous for the Nile River and pyramids">Ancient Egypt</span> (Nile River), <span class="key-word" data-def="One of the oldest civilizations, located in modern-day Iraq between the Tigris and Euphrates rivers">Mesopotamia</span> (Iraq), <span class="key-word" data-def="Ancient civilization in modern India/Pakistan along the Indus River">Indus Valley</span>, and <span class="key-word" data-def="Ancient civilization along the Yellow River in modern China">Ancient China</span>.`,
