       text:`<span class="key-word" data-def="The physical parts of a computer you can touch — screen, keyboard, chips">Hardware</span> is everything you can physically touch. <span class="key-word" data-def="Programs and applications that run on hardware — you can't touch software">Software</span> is the programs that run on hardware. Without software, hardware is useless — like a book with no words!`}
