  algorithms:{
    title:'Algorithms & Logic', readTime:'7 min',
    chunks:[
      {type:'intro', heading:'⚙️ What is an Algorithm?',
       text:`An <span class="key-word" data-def="A step-by-step set of instructions to solve a problem or complete a task">algorithm</span> is a set of instructions to solve a problem. You follow algorithms every day! A recipe is an algorithm. A morning routine is an algorithm. Computers need very precise algorithms.`,
