      {type:'intro', heading:'🗺️ What is a Map?',
       text:`A <span class="key-word" data-def="A scaled-down representation of an area drawn from above, showing features like roads, rivers and mountains">map</span> is a drawing that represents a real place from above. Maps help us navigate, understand geography, and plan journeys. Different types of maps serve different purposes.`,
